Package: champagnebourleaumarc
Type: Package
Title: Modeling of Champagne Glass
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Marc", "Bourleau", email = "marc.bourleau@unil.ch",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <marc.bourleau@unil.ch>
Description: This package is useful to compute the volume of a glass of champagne. It uses disk integration method and represents the glass as a solid of revolution. 
